  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1741_ncd_hin_r.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="hin" type="invocation" rend="top centre"><p>राम</p></div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1"  xml:id="trans_div1"><p><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_ram">Ram</ref></p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="hin" type="authorisation" rend="top centre">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
               श्री पांडुरंग चरणात सर
               <persName ref="#sadashivPandit">सदासीव राम</persName>
               नीरंतर
            </mentioned></stamp></p>   
         </div> 
         <div corresp="#orig_div2"  xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p>
               <stamp type="seal">Square black ink seal<mentioned><persName ref="#sadashivPandit">Sadashiv Ram</persName>,<note>Based on context, Sadashiv Ram is likely the same person as Sadashiv Pandit mentioned in other contemporary documents and has therefore been encoded as the same person.</note> 
               whose head is always bowed to the feet of Shri <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_panduranga">Panduranga</ref></mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="hin" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>राजश्री पंडत
               <persName ref="#sesadriRam">सेसाद्री राम जी</persName>
                मुका-
               <lb/>सदार <choice>
                  <abbr>प्र.</abbr>
                  <expan>परगना</expan>
               </choice> 
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">धार</placeName> 
               आगो 
               <persName ref="#bijaySingh">बीजे सींघ</persName>
               <lb/>वगेरा असवार ९ नव कुं चाकर
               <lb/>रखे दर माहा
               <choice>
                  <abbr>रु.</abbr>
                  <expan>रुपये</expan>
               </choice>
               <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="149">१४९</measure>
               <g ref="#ali">[अळी]</g>
               अंके
               <lb/>एक सव ओगण पचास ठह-
               <lb/>राया सो अड़ाही रोजा दर माहा
               <lb/>मीना कर बाकी माह बमाह पाये
               <lb/>जाय अर अपनी खातीर जमा सु
               <lb/>रात दीन चवकी पहरा गसत सुवारी
               <lb/><choice>
               <abbr>मो</abbr>
               <expan>मौज</expan>
               </choice>
               बेउजर हाजीर रहै हाजरी गैर
               <lb/>हाजरी तलब मो कठगी
               <lb/>मसारनीले सुवार <unclear>१</unclear>
               <lb/>३० 
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div3"  xml:id="trans_div3">  
            <p>
               <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_rajashri">Rajashri</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pandit">Pandit</ref> <persName ref="#sesadriRam">Sesadri Ram</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_mokasadar">mokasadar</ref> of
               <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, it is ordered that [since] <persName ref="#bijaySingh">Bijay Singh</persName>
               <lb/>etc., 9 [or in words] nine, horsemen have been employed,
               <lb/>between them the [salary] of <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="149">149</measure> <g ref="#ali">[fractional symbol]</g> rupees per month,
               <lb/>[or in words] one hundred and forty nine is fixed.
               <lb/>So pay two and a half [rupees] daily wages between them
               <lb/>[each] month [and] the rest they will receive monthly.
               <lb/>And being content,
               <lb/>they should guard the station night and day
               <lb/>and be present in the village without excuse. Absences will
               <lb/>be deducted from the salary.
               <lb/>The said horseman <unclear>1</unclear>
               <lb/>30 
            </p> 
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="mar" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <choice>
                  <abbr>त||</abbr>
                  <expan>तारीख</expan>
               </choice>
               <date><choice>
                  <abbr>छ</abbr>
                  <expan>चंद्र</expan>
               </choice>
               १ माहे जीहेज</date>
            </p></div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4"><p>On the lunar date of <date>1st of the month Zu al-Hijjah</date></p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="hin" type="particulars" rend="bottom">
            <p>
               <lb/> मसारनीले सुवार १
               <lb/><persName ref="#bidraban">बीदराबन</persName> सुवार १
               <lb/><persName ref="#nathuRam">नाथुराम</persName> सुवार १
               <lb/><persName ref="#lalSingh">लालसींघ</persName> सुवार १
               <lb rend="empty"/> <lb/><persName ref="#kanakSingh">कनकसींघ</persName> सुवार १
               <lb/><persName ref="#mohkamSingh">मोहकमसींघ</persName> सुवार १
               <lb/><persName ref="#kushalSingh">कुसलसींघ</persName> सुवार १
               <lb/><persName ref="#suratSingh">सुरतसींघ</persName> सुवार १
               <lb rend="empty"/> <lb/><unclear><persName ref="#gayadasa">गयादासा</persName></unclear> <choice><abbr>सु</abbr><expan>सुवार</expan></choice>
               <figure/>
            </p>   
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div5" xml:id="trans_div5">
            <p>
               <lb/>The said horseman [<persName ref="#bijaySingh">Bijay Singh</persName>] 1
               <lb/><persName ref="#bidraban">Bidraban</persName> horseman 1
               <lb/><persName ref="#nathuRam">Nathu Ram</persName> horseman 1
               <lb/><persName ref="#lalSingh">Lal Singh</persName> horseman 1
               <lb rend="empty"/> <lb/><persName ref="#kanakSingh">Kanak Singh</persName> horseman 1
               <lb/><persName ref="#mohkamSingh">Mohkam Singh</persName> horseman 1
               <lb/><persName ref="#kushalSingh">Kushal Singh</persName> horseman 1
               <lb/><persName ref="#suratSingh">Surat Singh</persName> horseman 1
               <lb rend="empty"/> <lb/><unclear><persName ref="#gayadasa">Gayadasa</persName></unclear> horseman <figure><figDesc>Two diagonal slashes and a loop, repeated three times.</figDesc></figure><note>It is unclear what this figure means.</note>
            </p>
         </div>   
         
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1741_brd_ncd_hin_v.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="mar" type="clericalNotes" rend="top">
            <p>
               <lb/>इसम नवीसी <choice>
                  <abbr>ब||</abbr>
                  <expan>बेनाव</expan>
               </choice>
               <persName ref="#bijaySingh">बीजे सीग</persName>
               <choice>
                  <abbr>ज||र</abbr>
                  <expan>जमादार</expan>
               </choice> वगैरे
               <lb/>स्वार ९ नव <unclear>मर्द</unclear> दर माहे 
               <choice>
                  <abbr>रुये</abbr>
                  <expan>रुपये</expan>
               </choice>
               <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="149">१४९</measure>
               <g ref="#ali">[अळी]</g>
               <lb/>येकसे येकून पनास
               <choice>
                  <abbr>रुये</abbr>
                  <expan>रुपये</expan>
               </choice>
               <gap/>
               <lb/>केले नौकरी सुरु 
               <date calendar="#suhur"><choice><abbr>छ</abbr>
                  <expan>चंद्र</expan></choice>
               १ जीलहेज 
               <choice><abbr>सु||</abbr>
               <expan>सुहूर</expan></choice>
               <lb/>
               इहिदे आर्बैन मया अलफ</date>
               <stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
                  मोर्तब सुद
               </mentioned></stamp>
            </p>   
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div6" xml:id="trans_div6">
            <p>
               <lb/>It is written in the name of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jamadar">jamadar</ref> <persName ref="#bijaySingh">Bijay Singh</persName> etc.,
               <lb/>that nine horsemen at the monthly [salary] of <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="149">149</measure> rupees, 
               <lb/>[or in words] one hundred and forty nine rupees, 
               <lb/>have been employed. On the lunar date of <date calendar="#suhur">1 Zu al-Hijjah in the Suhur year 
               <lb/>one thousand and one hundred and forty-one</date>. <stamp type="seal">Square black ink seal<mentioned>Verified.</mentioned></stamp>
            </p>   
         </div>
      </body>
  </text>
